posting_body: ['Take advantage of this amazing special.', 'Don’t miss out on this one-time special pricing from $999- $1499 on selected apartments', 'This community is in Houston at 1000 Country Place Dr.\xa0\xa0in the 77079 area.', 'Selection from various 2- and 3-bedroom floor plans options with prices that beats the competition.', "Our lovely community offers amenities and features that you'll enjoy.", 'These include high-speed internet access, renovated gym, and an amazing spacious swimming pool.', "It's time to love where you live.", 'Stop by for a visit us today.', '-Separate Shower', '-Fitness Center', '-Laundry Facilities', '-Swimming Pool', '-Tile Backsplash on selected homes', '-Walk-In Closet', '-Close to Shopping', '-2 Inch Fauxwood Blinds', '-Pet friendly', '-Washer and Dryer connections on selected homes', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'and ask for Selena and Jessica or you can also send us an email to\xa0Amalfi at bluestonepremier dot com', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '- Near Thornwood Elementary,', 'Spring Forest Middle School, Spring branch High School (Award Winning ISD School).', '- Near Memorial City Mall.', 'The Park at Amalfi', '1000 Country Place Dr.', 'Houston, Texas 77079', '***PRICES AND AVAILABILITY ARE SUBJECT TO CHANGE***', '***PICTURES MAY NOT REFLECT ACTUAL APARTMENT***', '*** WE COMPLY WITH EQUAL OPPORTUNITY HOUSING***']
